settings.description: A remixed version of those hand trap stages from SMB3 world 8, just a bit harder..
Bowser has taken control of the plains! Defeat his army and claim the plains!
The 'Ultimate" airship is hare! You must board it and get through it, then fight Boom Boom, the airship creator! Don't die or you will be forced to restart, he is a lot harder this time!
Didn't playtest it but it MAY be possible if you're very careful...
